<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Johann II. von Nassau-Wiesbaden-Idstein, Erzbischof von Mainz, Johann II. von Brunn, Bischof von Würzburg, Johann von Hohenlohe, Johann II., Graf von Wertheim, Konrad IX. von Weinsberg, und Thomas, Graf von Rieneck</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Geleit für die Nürnberger Kaufleute auf dem Weg zu und von der Frankfurter Herbstmesse.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_498"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_498_r1l11">Bẏſchoff cʒu Meincʒ </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_498_r1l12"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / VVir biten <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> hochwirdikeit mit <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiſʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_498_r1l13">daʒ ewr gnade vnſer <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> vnd kauffleute vnd auch Jr hab </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_498_r1l14">vnd kauffmanſchaft vnd die Jren in die nehſtkünftigen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_498_r1l15">frankfurter herbſtmeſſe vnd wıder darauſʒ mit geleẏte </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_498_r1l16">gnedıklich <expan>fürſeh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wölle / Alſo <expan>vven<ex>n</ex></expan> ſie oder die Jren darümb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_498_r1l17">cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden / oder aber den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> kumen vnd des begeren </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_498_r1l18">daʒ ſie vnd daʒ Jr <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> durch ewr land herſchaft vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_498_r1l19">gepiete ſıcher geleytet werden / Als vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> etc das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_498_r1l20">vnd biten des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnedıg 
<del rend="strikethrough">lich </del> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>Antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>vvid<ex>er</ex></expan> bey <expan>dıſe<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_498_r1l21"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> dıener / <expan>Sc<ex>ri</ex>pt<ex>um</ex></expan> in die <expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>ı</expan> Oſwaldi Anno xij<hi rend="sup">o</hi></ab>
<note place="bottomcentral"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_498_line_1576398158104_75"><expan>No<ex>ta</ex></expan> daʒ man <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Bẏſſch<ex>of</ex></expan> von <expan>wircʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_498_line_1576398164612_80">hewr niht <expan>geſ<ex>chriben</ex></expan> hat vmb geleyte </ab> </del>
<ab facs="#facs_498_r1l26"><expan>No<ex>ta</ex></expan> <expan>q<ex>uaeque</ex></expan> forma <expan>p<ex>rae</ex>ſc<ex>ri</ex>pta</expan> von <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> geleite et antiqua <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> retro <expan>ſc<ex>ri</ex>pta</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_498_r1l27">ambe in <expan>Co<ex>n</ex>ſılio</expan> <expan>ſu<ex>n</ex>t</expan> audite et illa noua <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> eſt approbata etc </ab>
</note>
</div>
<div type="similiter"><pb facs="#facs_499"/>
<ab facs="#facs_499_r1l1">Biſchof cʒu vvircʒburg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_499_r1l2">
<del rend="strikethrough">Lücʒen S Tanner Amptman cʒu der <expan>Newe<ex>n</ex>ſtat</expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_499_r1l3"><expan>Johan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒu hohenloch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_499_r1l4"><expan>Johan<ex>n</ex></expan> Grafen cʒu wertheim </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_499_r1l5"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒu <expan>weınſp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_499_r1l6"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Thoman Grafen cʒu Ryeneck </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_499_r1l7"><expan>ſı<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> ut <expan>ep<ex>iscop</ex>o</expan> <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex>dict<ex>o</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_499_r1l8"><expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan> <expan>mutand<ex>is</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_498"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Byschoff czu Meincz </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir biten <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
                        hochwirdikeit mit <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz, daz ewr gnade unser
                                <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> und kauffleute und auch ir hab und
                        kauffmanschaft und die iren in die nehstkünftigen frankfurter herbstmesse
                        und wider darausz mit geleyte gnediklich <expan>fürseh<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wölle, also <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> sie oder die iren darümb czu
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden oder aber den
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> kumen und des begeren, daz sie und daz
                        ir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> durch ewr land herschaft und gepiete sicher
                        geleytet werden, als wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> etc. Das
                                <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Und biten des
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnedig
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> bey <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> diener.
                            <expan>Sc<ex>ri</ex>pt<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                                <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Oswaldi anno xii<hi rend="sup">o</hi>. <app>
<note place="bottomcentral">
<expan>No<ex>ta</ex></expan>
<expan>q<ex>uaeque</ex></expan> forma
                                                  <expan>p<ex>rae</ex>sc<ex>ri</ex>pta</expan> von
                                                  <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> geleite et antiqua
                                                  <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> retro
                                                  <expan>sc<ex>ri</ex>pta</expan> ambe in
                                                  <expan>co<ex>n</ex>silio</expan>
<expan>su<ex>n</ex>t</expan> audite et illa nova
                                                  <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> est approbata etc. </note>
</app></ab></div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><pb facs="#facs_499"/>Bischof czu Wirczburg,<lb/>
<expan>Johan<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czu hohenloch,<lb/>
<expan>Johan<ex>n,</ex></expan> grafen czu
